Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.13,0:00:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.94,0:00:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角 追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.48,0:00:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.29,0:00:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.96,0:00:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.17,0:00:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.75,0:01:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.32,0:01:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.26,0:01:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.86,0:01:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.73,0:01:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.33,0:01:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S．A．C．2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.18,0:02:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果我們還是跟事實無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.45,0:02:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在找贖罪的機會也是事實啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.16,0:02:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對亞裔各國來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.76,0:02:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受過上個世紀戰後教育的人也許更是如此呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面對亞裔和歐洲的戰爭袖手旁觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.44,0:02:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面卻在各地打第二次越南戰爭也是相同的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.74,0:02:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有這個救濟基金的數字也是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.98,0:02:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經不能再喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這個也當成稅金不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是說不過會長呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住...住手 基諾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒...饒了我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求...求求你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基諾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基諾，你怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晃動稍微大了一點哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常抱歉 會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#02飽食終日的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.99,0:03:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要去那家店吃牡蠣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可是極品哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我有點事 今天就不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 又是你那個正職嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可悲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.74,0:04:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用人工內臟的義體人根本不需要食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況對全部感覺器官都數字化的他來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.41,0:04:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,享受美食的這種行為不過只是一種懷念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.36,0:04:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又被公安盯上了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說中松的事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說又被甩了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.77,0:04:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,義體人專用食品...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仔細想想他們其實也是受害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.18,0:04:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被徽召去打通稱為第二次越南載爭的第四次非核大載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.11,0:04:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依照從軍的規定動手術換上高性能電子腦和部分義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.49,0:05:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家常銳「載爭就是跨國企業的商品展示會「
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.59,0:05:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使電子腦化、義體化技術獲得飛躍進步的實驗場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是上次大戰的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們沒有發現自己曾是白老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在失去自己的身體、家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至是國土的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.57,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊緊抓住微薄的給付以及分配到的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乍看之下好像正在享受幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.38,0:05:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就不知道這是從電子腦和義體構成的虛擬人格中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.61,0:05:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,產生出來的虛假快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,針對招慰難民居住區的連續爆炸案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警視廳聯合搜查本部剛剛宣佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.79,0:05:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾收到個別主義者的恐怖組織所發出的犯罪聲明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.03,0:05:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據聲明來看該組織要求亞裔難民離開日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且把他們一連串的犯罪行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,界定為對亞裔難民主導的暴動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.84,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和難民救濟措施導致的財政缺口所做的報復行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.11,0:06:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媒盟只會照單全收當局發表的內容然後報導出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.21,0:06:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明知是謊言 卻還是操縱情報獲取利益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是他們的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.76,0:06:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媒體希望得到什麼 想要去嘗試些什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.96,0:06:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要窺視一下他們的夜生活就可以知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.57,0:06:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們連客觀判斷自己所為是否 已然沉溺於享樂的能力都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.94,0:06:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是不斷嘲笑愚昧的一般民眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要看三大網絡的會長片倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.96,0:06:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何評論在高級日式餐廳天天聚餐的人 一切就很清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合執政黨黨代表階級的不必說一定有份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.03,0:06:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有掌握各省廳高級官僚身上電子腦和義體專利權的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那群跨國企業幹部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.47,0:07:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,片倉根本沒有報導真相的氣概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.74,0:07:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有的只是維持自己帝國的慾望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(新濱市上空)(失火的政府大樓)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(政府大樓遭到攻擊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現場仍然冒著濃煙(於政府大樓前線報導)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彷彿訴說著反對難民政策的亞裔難民所主導的官署攻擊行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,規模相當大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下手不夠重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣根本無法了結任何事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也無法讓任何事情開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.71,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Reset The world
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媒體才是真正的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.38,0:07:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙跟執政當局連手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.55,0:07:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大聲地假裝自己是正義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他們不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏有個知道一切的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.19,0:07:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個知道真相並決心達成理想的堅強意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須盡快執行他的死刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是上天賦予知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.97,0:08:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且為了探求真相無謂死亡之人的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.32,0:08:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上個世紀初 一位偉大的猶太作家曾這樣說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能存在沒有真實的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂真實恐怕就是人生本身吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.93,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這裏才存在著真實的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.95,0:08:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的美麗毫無疑問就是真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種身為一個生命體的毫無修飾的美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有把快樂當成快樂來享受的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.23,0:09:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有為了生存而切割出來 沒有參雜任何多餘事物的純潔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.03,0:09:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一看就知道她全身都是義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.54,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她完美的肉體無法跟特化用來享樂的目的切割開來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才是美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.31,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我確信只有她才是真正的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.19,0:09:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她身上可以看到某種為了維護身為人的尊嚴而頑強保護的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.44,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在她的精神面前任何東西都黯淡無光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.14,0:09:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算發揮金錢的力量把她得到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.51,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不可能得到她的意志、美麗以及真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.24,0:10:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論什麼人都不可能佔有真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使他們使用權利威嚇我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且想要玩弄我們的心靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一個人知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而那個人除了我之外別無他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.99,0:11:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天世界將在真實中醒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天終於到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要請假就說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道你那是正職還是兼職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.81,0:11:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安排片倉會長專屬駕駛員這種高級工作給你可是你的榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的技術的確是最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是大戰時的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 我告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.39,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你們這種傷殘戰鬥義體人原本就沒有什麼工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前你不是這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.20,0:12:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候的你至少擁有面對真實的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是以前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.04,0:12:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會放任片倉那樣的人為所欲為才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.55,0:12:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時...時代不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了活下去不得不這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.85,0:12:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經忘記我為什麼離開軍隊跟隨你到現在了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你有沒有在聽啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛剛在嘀咕什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊的事就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看對方的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咋天很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.92,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擅自請假沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這回事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.87,0:13:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 沒事 另外...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明需要我的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻故意裝成一副不記得的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個有虐待狂的混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.16,0:13:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我稍微謙虛一下他就得寸進尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.83,0:13:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你們這種人只要我動一下操縱桿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心中沒有一絲猶豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.85,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不吝於為可憐的大眾奉獻生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.15,0:13:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 就算我將片倉從這個世界除去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.63,0:14:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是害怕這件事情會被那些傢伙的網絡掩蓋起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果變成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.77,0:14:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相就不會傳達到世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.97,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了不發生這種事有必要把真相先告訴某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老婆變得不聽我的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是糟糕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.35,0:14:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你得好好服務一下哄她高興才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾陪我喝一杯怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.46,0:14:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不然去你之前說過吃得到牡蠣的那家店也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真難得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒什麼啦 老實說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.30,0:14:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子我最近就不得不為了那個正職辭掉這份工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.34,0:14:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 你陞官啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是令人羨慕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.71,0:14:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 也不是那樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.31,0:14:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是這個原因的話 我實在很想陪你去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是今天實在沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就算了 沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.07,0:15:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了虛無飄渺的目的 以及維護一部分人的權力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.04,0:15:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被迫奔向戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.44,0:15:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰都無法理解我在那裏失去的東西有多巨大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想用這些錢買下她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.67,0:15:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼一點根本不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.28,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰爭當中失去重要事物的不只有你一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.46,0:16:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是什麼都還沒做嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下去的要另外收錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我付訂金的時候不是連入會金都交了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是那些錢被拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的老婆孩子就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.50,0:16:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒...沒有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飯吃了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.80,0:17:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您好 這裏是招慰難民救濟基金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.44,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是響應你們幕款的人(目前在日本有失去祖國的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝您平日的照顧(300萬難民)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...因為出了點事情(現在正是展現互助精神的時候)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不可以中止對你們的轉帳匯款?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.55,0:17:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉無法識別你的申請事項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想中止對你們的匯款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想取消登記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.26,0:18:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我為您從頭介紹申請手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要詢問申請基金的事項請按1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.91,0:18:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的詢問事項請按2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久違的一場壓倒性勝利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.71,0:18:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 你說那場選代表的比賽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.78,0:18:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那記右鉤拳真是厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感動死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會想吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.59,0:18:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是不需要嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會想吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是不需要嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?為什麼?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.04,0:18:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會想吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是本能 這不是真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是嚇了我一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.61,0:18:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到那傢伙會被公安抓走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是不是早就知道那傢伙是亞裔的人了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基諾啊 他們不是很熟嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎麼可能會知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.00,0:19:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.07,0:19:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞裔難民主導的官署攻擊事件已經抓到實施犯罪的嫌犯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三澤陽一 又名楊岷台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.38,0:19:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在被警官銬住雙手帶出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是確信將會勝利的手勢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.19,0:19:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼...會是他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逮捕這次實施犯罪的嫌犯後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.46,0:19:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經有三個"亞裔難民支持團體"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及"招慰難民人權及保障協會"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,召開了前所未見的記者會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們發表聲明表示他的行為是替每天遭受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.27,0:19:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無理歧視的亞洲、日本雙方難民發出抗議的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.57,0:19:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一連串的犯罪行為按其情節 尚有斟酌的餘地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故 意求減輕刑責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.49,0:20:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你送一下這位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.85,0:20:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,片倉對你做了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在找你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這幾天一直都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.37,0:20:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 應該說從還沒出生以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會再讓你遇到痛苦的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就這樣兩個人一起到遠方去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到一個誰都無法打擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只屬於我們的國度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.25,0:21:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 在那之前我有件事情無論如何一定要去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.79,0:21:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必須...解放真實才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶著我一起嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.61,0:21:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經拚命戰鬥過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你勝利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.72,0:21:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是那樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.30,0:21:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛接到石川的聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.11,0:22:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙似乎跟這一連串的恐怖活動無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.91,0:22:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據他在軍中的經歷他失去下半身跟作戰行動無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.55,0:22:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是在當地染上了一種惡性的性病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.52,0:22:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 少校 你有在聽嗎?
