Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.76,0:22:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要怎麼處理那傢伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.43,0:22:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.90,0:22:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對現實抱著一點希望和焦躁的不特定多數人中的一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.11,0:22:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會把計劃付諸實施的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.41,0:22:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.94,0:22:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我該送您到哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.92,0:22:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對真相無知到可悲的無產階級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.48,0:23:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.12,0:23:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.66,0:23:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在顯示當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.66,0:23:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
